{"tid":51630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】曾俊華上高登！！！！！！！","createTime":"2016-12-23T11:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T22:23:59.000Z","uid":5812,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26947d0dc20711d82bdb804203b7df63c03fb329","tid":51630,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/192039_8d430649e5a2aaaa65fd2c064580ecf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F192039_8d430649e5a2aaaa65fd2c064580ecf7.jpg&h=2a44713e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深水埗有包羅萬有的鴨記、美味的腸粉、米芝連點心，更令人欣賞是這裡濃厚的人情味。<br />\n<br />\n今日再訪深水埗，探訪經營社企的朋友，與街坊近距離接觸，又品嘗了不同美食，體會這裏的人情和活力。<br />\n<br />\n#深水埗 #鴨寮街 #SVhk #社企 #高登 #JohnTsang"},{"pid":"1495f36666d698a0f2891ebccb4d93846ab71655","tid":51630,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:40:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d54eebd1487023b8e878d8d2cc04eeb64b7eaa5","tid":51630,"uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:47:03.000Z","msg":"無人care高登 包括個電腦商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fe68e40eca8c97978f54d2f5f05c894392b78b","tid":51630,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:47:29.000Z","msg":"好特首出遊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e3f59cb6a1a9c847370c96e3840e85e9789002","tid":51630,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc546585d254190b58c05bb51a0e97bc2ea851db","tid":51630,"uid":14076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"有邊個（前）高官敢唔帶保鏢出街⋯"},{"pid":"d4dd0d62c08c8c076b0d047ae5350c54d0f16111","tid":51630,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re